# Pre-Merge Quality Gates

- After meaningful code changes, run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` before asking for commit/PR.
- Fix introduced lint/type/build issues in changed files first.
- Keep generated-map updates separate from app-logic updates when preparing commits.
- If validation is skipped due to time or environment limits, explicitly report what was not verified.
